						               													<description>Will you survive? Roll-Z is a Solo Survival Time Challenge, in Print and Play format, but with colorfull high definition PDF files, and that's not all! You will need the Oficial Game Aplication that not only complements game immersion, with chilling original music, sounds and graphics, it also enhance the gameplay WITH RANDOM ENCOUNTERS making it a REAL TIME CHALLENGE.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Roll-Z you represent a survivor who must find pieces to fix the car, place them, and at the same time repel a horde of zombies trying to tear down your fragile barricade. Is not easy! If you manage to repair the old Chevy (by putting together the 5 necessary pieces) before time runs out, you have won, but if your barricade collapses or you run out of time, you will became another brainless wobblers.&amp;#10;TO SURVIVE, you will need to master all the resources of the game, from zombies to trash. With an easy to learn mechanic, and a deep fast paced tactic options, you get a replayable surviving game to play with all your friends. Challenge them all!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
